info.description:
====================
Products.CMFResource
====================

Products.CMFResource replaces the portal form form validation mechanism from Plone.
It should work just fine in plain CMFForm as well.

Features
--------

- Can be bullet points


Installation
------------

Install Products.CMFResource by adding it to your buildout::

    [buildout]

    ...

    eggs =
        Products.CMFResource


and then running ``bin/buildout``
